# Helm packages everything in the chart directory into the release secret.
# These subdirectories are applied by separate Flux Kustomizations and must
# not be included in the flux-addons chart bundle — they'd inflate the release
# secret by hundreds of KB (CRD manifests alone are ~500KB) and push the
# rendered release over the 1MB Kubernetes Secret limit.
crd-manifests/
mattermost-workspace/
